Package: roughVizR
Type: Package
Title: Hand-Drawn, Sketchy Data Visualizations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ashwin", "Malshe", email = "ashwin.malshe@utsa.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jared", "Wilber", role = c("aut", "cph"), comment = "roughViz.js library")
    )
Description: Create hand-drawn, sketchy styled charts including bar charts, 
    horizontal bar charts, donut charts, line charts, pie charts, scatter plots, 
    and stacked bar charts. Based on the roughViz.js JavaScript library which 
    uses D3.js and rough.js.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ashgreat/roughVizR
BugReports: https://github.com/ashgreat/roughVizR/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    htmlwidgets (>= 0.8)
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    htmltools,
    shiny,
    testthat (>= 3.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
